{"tid":1708012,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有鑑於已經有兩人被實彈擊中，我想講少少有關鎗械既基本常識","createTime":"2019-11-11T12:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T16:02:58.000Z","uid":18672,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"65847150884020ead4beea1fa62a1d2529215e2b","tid":1708012,"uid":18672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:36:40.000Z","msg":"1. 準備拔鎗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1no39rg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1no39rg.png&h=913cfa8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ruOvPrZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FruOvPrZ.jpg&h=0ea33e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果冇明確既口頭警告，應該將此動作視為<span style=\"color: red;\">第一個警告</span><br />\n任何人（即使係受過訓練既專業人士）都唔應該覺得自己有能力阻止其他人拔鎗<br />\n係特殊情況下，由拔鎗到瞄準射擊只需要0.5秒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g11oE_nxWSU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg11oE_nxWSU&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQQg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=a61b14a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g11oE_nxWSU</a><br />\n（牛仔射擊比賽）<br />\n<br />\n情況許可既情況下，<span style=\"color: red;\">應該慢慢後退，直到有掩護物</span><br />\n<br />\n2. 鎗口指住人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pTBUwHH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpTBUwHH.png&h=5569eccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c41tBbe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc41tBbe.png&h=aef91af7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當鎗口指住人，如果仍然係冇明確既口頭警告，<span style=\"color: red;\">應該假設射手隨時有可能射擊亦係最後一個警告</span><br />\n電影好多時有特工被人用手鎗指住時搶走該把鎗既場面<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家千其唔好模仿</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你不幸被人用鎗指住，<span style=\"color: red;\">請你立即舉高雙手企係原地等射手既指示，只有特殊情況下你應該慢慢後退</span><br />\n如果你見到有人被人用鎗指住，而你就係個個人附近，<span style=\"color: red;\">請你立即舉高雙手慢慢後退</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">除此之外，大家亦都應該要時刻留意是否有人做出以上的動作</span></span>"},{"pid":"2fa417215462de8c57525657dcc07e87cc5f4fda","tid":1708012,"uid":34990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:38:00.000Z","msg":"3個呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30790812dc3ff9a15f8e8d4236625c43b379927e","tid":1708012,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90dbd34f8e988e19beca3c4f50515497a9986fad","tid":1708012,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:39:04.000Z","msg":"你講緊只適用於一般人拔槍，警察唔使守武力守則？"},{"pid":"8e542be8dfed0659adf1f4a627e704910dc62e77","tid":1708012,"uid":18672,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"90dbd34f8e988e19beca3c4f50515497a9986fad","tid":1708012,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:39:04.000Z","msg":"你講緊只適用於一般人拔槍，警察唔使守武力守則？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:43:06.000Z","msg":"如果人地純粹係想射你，你做乜都唔會改變到個結果"},{"pid":"cf4fb281bd1e6650e6ea17ae0ec22d125493e871","tid":1708012,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e542be8dfed0659adf1f4a627e704910dc62e77","tid":1708012,"uid":18672,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"90dbd34f8e988e19beca3c4f50515497a9986fad","tid":1708012,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:39:04.000Z","msg":"你講緊只適用於一般人拔槍，警察唔使守武力守則？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:43:06.000Z","msg":"如果人地純粹係想射你，你做乜都唔會改變到個結果"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:47:28.000Z","msg":"咁你打咁大堆野又有咩用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=